{
  "texts": [
    "Equation (19) represents the formula for fully connected layer.",
    "where X' is input, Y 'is Output, W is the Weight and b is the bias.",
    "The three gated units that comprise the bulk of the LSTM neural network are the forget gate, i/p gate, and o/p gate.",
    "The i/p gate is the main processor of i/p data.",
    "The forget gate controls how well the current cell remembers prior information."
  ]
}